Jia Cong agreed, and those little sisters play, it was time for lunch.



Purples led the servant girls to come up and remove the candies and cakes from the table and wipe them clean. Then dishes were brought up and placed on the table.



There are ginger sauce fish fillet, spiced rice pigeon, sweet-and-sour lotus root slices, shredded chicken and white fungus, osmanthus flower fish sticks, eight treasure rabbit diced, stewed deer tendon in casserole, chrysanthemum tenderloin, fried quail, Braised red scallop, Braised fish skin with scallion, sliced Suckling pig and more than 20 dishes.
